{"tid":756981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輸了接力賽　國中女生PO「輸到脫褲」照","createTime":"2018-07-26T12:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T14:10:58.000Z","uid":1121,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"12811b766ab8bb1063a5317ca2ed66dd8bb3ecac","tid":756981,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">建立時間：2013/12/14 15:56</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20131214/640_e42627afb20246f3f55b542e9fbf6215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20131214%2F640_e42627afb20246f3f55b542e9fbf6215.jpg&h=adeaad72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【徐彩媚／嘉義報導】嘉義某國中昨天舉行運動會，女學生疑是班上大隊接力比賽成績不理想，在臉書PO「輸到脫褲」的照片，背景是學校操場，圖中兩名女學生，身穿運動服，旁邊還有男同學，只見這兩名女學生滿面笑容的將體育長褲，脫到小腿位置，露出一截腿肉，意謂著真的輸很慘，一旁還有男生在看，有網友看了認為學生很有創意，但有讀者覺得不妥向《蘋果》投訴。 該校校長指出，學校昨天舉行校慶運動會，不過就算輸了，也不該有此行為，會先了解學生動機，再協助她們對事物的處理尺度。下午校方連繫到學生，她們表示，有穿安全底褲，當時只是用比較誇張的方式來達，後來覺得不妥，凌晨就撤下該張照片了，對於PO照感到很後悔。"},{"pid":"1198e16b79e2ca711b3be085fe3a5abc9e1edee0","tid":756981,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b821494d0c5975f6483ec0a178ae07cfaed956","tid":756981,"uid":155818,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"國中生<br />\n初中生<br />\n可食用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b55e86ff61fa78430791d6c88284cc984ec122","tid":756981,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ad0e0bafa2c8109219e7dcf2c42197821a325f","tid":756981,"uid":1779,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:24:34.000Z","msg":"台妹真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/